title: EP 138: JOSH POTTER - Go For It! Now What?
description: This week I have Comedian Josh Potter who has just moved to LA from Buffalo. He's right in the thick of some major life changes and was kind enough to share his hopes, fears, anxieties and insights on his journey. It's an exciting time in someone's life when they take the leap. Here's a look at what it's like to be in the eye of the storm!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
